I"y<p>The Mirror of Einan was a prison to Einan the Black for nearly one hundred years. Ulrach and Lem were able to use it to communicate with him. At first, neither party could hear the other, but Einan guided Lem through a blood ritual to allow them to speak.</p>

<p>Einan desired freedom, but was willing to demonstrate to Lem that he could be trusted, granting him power</p>
